For this month's #YourLast5Photos, @charliefplummer walks us through the recent images in his camera roll after driving cross country with his best friend @delwatergap: 

About the photographs, he writes: "These photos represent the serendipity of a few big themes in my life meeting up to create a dreamy moment in time that I’ll always hold close. Getting to work with one of my favorite writers in the world in one of my most precious places in the world is beyond special in itself. But when that writer also happens to be one of my best friends, it feels like going to the moon. These pictures are a reminder of that feeling and hopefully always will be."
